And then according to the Law of Intercalation, the Beasts Months are ſupplied by the Gentiles Months; becauſe the Beaſt had Time, Times and Half a Time;
               Or 1260 Days of Years. and he not coming into Succeſſion time enough for that Time, Times and Half a Time, the Months of the Gentiles, as his People, intercalate, or ſupply the Beaſt's Months; where they are to be ſupplied, and where there is Supply ready for them
                  Viz. At the 1260 days beginning; For as ſoon as the Time, Times, Half Time of the Beaſt begin in the Gentiles 42 Months, the 1260 Days begin alſo.: And then the Gentiles Months become one with the Beaſt's, as they muſt needs; becauſe Power was given to him over Tongues, People and Nations, as the Time, Times, Half Time were given to Him alſo.
